She sign that prenup?

997
00:38:52,703 --> 00:38:56,372
No, but she sent those
because she realized the prenup

998
00:38:56,424 --> 00:38:59,625
was about love,
not control.

999
00:38:59,627 --> 00:39:02,845
Then I respect her decision.

1000
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,263
What changed her mind
about me?

1001
00:39:04,298 --> 00:39:05,681
You really want to know?

1002
00:39:05,716 --> 00:39:07,032
- Mm-hmm.
- Jessica.

1003
00:39:07,068 --> 00:39:08,551
Oh, shit.
What did she say?

1004
00:39:08,603 --> 00:39:10,302
I got to know that secret.

1005
00:39:10,304 --> 00:39:11,554
I don't know
what she said to Rachel,

1006
00:39:11,606 --> 00:39:14,940
but I know
what she said to me.

1007
00:39:14,976 --> 00:39:16,942
So that's why you're here.

1008
00:39:16,978 --> 00:39:20,146
You know those people that
I told you I was fighting for?

1009
00:39:23,151 --> 00:39:25,451
Jessica's not
gonna go for it.

1010
00:39:25,486 --> 00:39:26,719
I get it.

1011
00:39:26,754 --> 00:39:29,288
Too much money to lay out
for too little payoff.

1012
00:39:29,323 --> 00:39:33,959
But you said you came from
the same place as these people.

1013
00:39:33,995 --> 00:39:38,247
Robert, they need someone
like you to fight for them,

1014
00:39:38,299 --> 00:39:41,133
and I can't do it.

1015
00:39:41,169 --> 00:39:43,752
So I'm asking you to.

1016
00:39:43,805 --> 00:39:45,045
You think this case
is a winner?

1017
00:39:45,056 --> 00:39:46,639
I do.

1018
00:39:48,176 --> 00:39:50,509
Then what do you say
we do it together?

1019
00:39:53,347 --> 00:39:54,680
What are you doing here,
Louis?

1020
00:39:54,682 --> 00:39:56,565
I notice you didn't come
to the vote this morning.

1021
00:39:56,601 --> 00:39:59,401
No, I didn't. I was busy
closing a deal for my client.

1022
00:39:59,437 --> 00:40:01,570
Let me guess. You had 'em
backdate your sale to yesterday,

1023
00:40:01,606 --> 00:40:03,022
so it falls
under your old pay structure?

1024
00:40:03,074 --> 00:40:04,674
No, Louis,
that's something you would do,

1025
00:40:04,692 --> 00:40:07,526
because unlike you, I don't
actually care about the money.

1026
00:40:07,528 --> 00:40:08,861
You expect me
to believe that?

1027
00:40:08,913 --> 00:40:10,446
I don't care whether you
believe it or not.

1028
00:40:10,498 --> 00:40:13,699
My compensation package
was about recognizing what I do.

1029
00:40:13,751 --> 00:40:15,034
Money was just a consequence.

1030
00:40:15,086 --> 00:40:16,752
That's why I didn't mind
sharing it with Donna.

1031
00:40:16,787 --> 00:40:18,254
- Now, get out.
- No.

1032
00:40:18,289 --> 00:40:21,090
You did care about the money,
because it was the last thing

1033
00:40:21,125 --> 00:40:23,092
you had that separated you
from me.

1034
00:40:23,127 --> 00:40:25,344
- Excuse me?
- I got name partner.

1035
00:40:25,379 --> 00:40:28,047
I got Donna,
and that drove you nuts.

1036
00:40:28,099 --> 00:40:30,132
So you shit on me
at the meeting,

1037
00:40:30,184 --> 00:40:32,101
and then you pretended
to apologize.

1038
00:40:32,136 --> 00:40:33,636
I did apologize, Louis.

1039
00:40:33,688 --> 00:40:35,221
I came to you
like a man,

1040
00:40:35,273 --> 00:40:37,973
and then when I gave you
the chance to make it up to me,

1041
00:40:38,025 --> 00:40:40,109
you choked,
like you always do.

1042
00:40:40,144 --> 00:40:41,477
Well, how you like me now?

1043
00:40:41,529 --> 00:40:43,779
Because the only thing you
had left was that you made more.

1044
00:40:43,814 --> 00:40:45,481
And now you don't,
and I win.

1045
00:40:45,533 --> 00:40:48,901
You didn't win anything.

1046
00:40:48,953 --> 00:40:50,286
What are you talking about?

1047
00:40:50,321 --> 00:40:53,405
I'm talking about the fact
that no matter what you get,

1048
00:40:53,457 --> 00:40:55,124
you're always wanting more.

1049
00:40:55,159 --> 00:40:57,459
And the problem
with always wanting more is

1050
00:40:57,495 --> 00:41:00,079
that the second you get it,
it can always be taken away.

1051
00:41:00,081 --> 00:41:01,330
You're not reversing
that vote.

1052
00:41:01,382 --> 00:41:02,715
I'm not talking
about the vote.

1053
00:41:02,750 --> 00:41:06,085
I'm talking
about what you value most.

1054
00:41:06,137 --> 00:41:07,137
That's right.

1055
00:41:07,138 --> 00:41:09,421
Might not happen today
or tomorrow,

1056
00:41:09,473 --> 00:41:12,258
but it's gonna happen, because
I'm gonna make it happen.

1057
00:41:12,310 --> 00:41:15,094
One day, you're gonna walk
into your office,

1058
00:41:15,146 --> 00:41:16,962
and she's gonna be gone.

